      "date": "2013-09-09 15:21:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nIMHO MGS failover nid should not be set by --mgsnode, but by --failnode. Because all nid by --mgsnode should be a primary nid.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "8cdd2d63ac87055711ad322f8ac82cb212949b18",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 103,
        "name": "Zhenyu Xu",
        "email": "bobijam@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "bobijam"
      },
      "date": "2013-09-09 15:27:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nmkfs_lustre.c does think --mgsnode is for mgs failnode\n\ncase 'm': {\n...\nmop->mo_mgs_failnodes++;\nbreak;\n}\n\nalso in lustre_start_mgc()\n\n/* Add any failover MGS nids */\ni = 1;\n...\nclass_find_param(ptr, PARAM_MGSNODE, &ptr) == 0))) {\n/* New failover node */\n...",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
